window.bookSummaryJSON = "Tananarive Due, author of <i>The Living Blood</i> won the American Book Award and is praised as Stephen King's equal by <i>Publishers Weekly</i>. In <i>The Good House</i>, Due sets a story of ancient powers and modern retribution in a small Pacific Northwest town. When a young woman returns to her grandmother's empty mansion, she is pitted against demonic forces that have poisoned her family for generations."; 
